title: Everybody F*cks With Me Pt. I with Guapdad 4000
description:
We’re whipping the sauce to get lost in this week! Throwing Fits is flossin’ with budding hip-hop superstar and viral legend, Guapdad 4000. Guap joins the boyz to run through his best in class AKAs, eulogize his scamming pedigree, break down Japanese fashion, explain how masturbation is self-care, review his favorite anime, what is was like meeting E-40, ranking his top 5 dead or alive, plus a surprise cameo from BJ The Chicago Kid and much more on part 1 of this Mount Rushmore episode of The Only Podcast This Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
